Building Fuse
-------------

This fork is CMake-only.

For supported dependency setup, build commands, smoke tests, and platform
notes, use these documents instead of historical autotools instructions:

* `BUILD-SDL3.md` for Linux and Windows builds
* `TESTING-SDL3.md` for runtime validation
* `RELEASE-SDL3.md` for release verification

Quick start on Linux:

```sh
sh ./scripts/build-linux.sh
cmake --install build-linux --prefix /usr/local
```

Quick start on Windows PowerShell:

```powershell
./scripts/build-windows.ps1
cmake --install build-win-native --prefix "$PWD/dist"
```

The maintained product in this repository is the SDL3 build of Fuse. Legacy
autotools, GTK/Xlib/framebuffer/SVGAlib build instructions, and MinGW/Cygwin
packaging flows are no longer supported by this fork.
